title: POLICE STORY -- Trigger Point ( with David Janssen, Don Johnson
description:
The episode guides are wrong. There is no "Season 5". This was the first of 
the 2 hour movie specials from that era after the Police Story series was cancelled in 1977. Eight more were produced over the next year & 1/2.


With David Janssen, Robert Forster, Diana Muldaur, Don Johnson, Meg Foster, 
Scott Hylands, Scott Brady, Milton Selzer, Jayne Kennedy, MacDonald Carey, 
Bob Hastings, and Edward James Olmos
